          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "11584",
      "label": "9",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "Show experience in camping by doing the following:"
        }
      ],
      "resources": [],
      "sub_requirements": [
        {
          "id": "11585",
          "label": "a",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Camp for at least 20 nights at designated Scouting activities or events. One long-term camping experience of up to six consecutive nights may be applied toward this requirement. Two nights may be counted toward the total for each additional long-term camping trip. Each night must be spent either under the sky, in a tent you have pitched yourself (if a tent is provided and already set up, you do not need to pitch your own), in a hammock that is safely strung outdoors, in a lean-to, or other three-sided shelter with an open front. Nights spent in indoor lock-in events, cabin camping, hotel stays, or other covered accommodations do not count toward the 20 nights."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "11586",
          "label": "b",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "On any of these camping experiences, you must do TWO of the following, only with proper preparation and under qualified supervision."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "11587",
          "label": "1",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Hike up a mountain, gaining at least 1,000 vertical feet."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [
            {
              "title": "Training for Elevation Gain (video)",
              "url": "https://youtu.be/wrAzopMgriU?si=POvk4jZLbzeTos5t"
            }
          ],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "11588",
          "label": "2",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Backpack, snowshoe, or cross-country ski for at least 4 miles."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [
            {
              "title": "Learn to Snowshoe (video)",
              "url": "https://youtu.be/bIylS8VFGcg?si=_C2XoAWrFGsx0bSa"
            }
          ],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "11589",
          "label": "3",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Take a bike trip of at least 15 miles or at least four hours."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [
            {
              "title": "What I Wish I Knew Before Bikepacking (video)",
              "url": "https://youtu.be/eC-XDuniSco?si=ThrPiNPJvBWOimjp"
            }
          ],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "11590",
          "label": "4",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Take a nonmotorized trip on the water of at least four hours or 5 miles."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [
            {
              "title": "Canoeing With LNT (video)",
              "url": "https://youtu.be/F8vjVVCf9YI?si=5TuRYuF6q8BjpESE"
            }
          ],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "11591",
          "label": "5",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Plan and carry out an overnight snow camping experience."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [
            {
              "title": "Winter Camping Tips (video)",
              "url": "https://youtu.be/ReanLLCCKIc?si=hlHXtTKcefLmsVuJ"
            }
          ],
          "sub_requirements": []
        },
        {
          "id": "11592",
          "label": "6",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "Rappel down a rappel route of 30 feet or more."
            }
          ],
          "resources": [
            {
              "title": "How to Rapel (video)",
              "url": "https://youtu.be/7U6tdEevJgs?si=Iq942pMfrehB7dIX"
